ssets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明哥篇反而幾鍾意<br />\n空島就覺得悶悶地<br />\n準備翻睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最記得敲起黃金鄉的大鐘同埋條細蛇一直守護住黃金鄉變成巨蛇<br />\n<br />\n證明堆狒狒無講大話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/214500_5893b813b47f1c5e2b56b2899c0817bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F214500_5893b813b47f1c5e2b56b2899c0817bd.jpg&h=2631b723&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n空島好撚好睇wor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搭上海流衝上空島嗰陣睇到手心出汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5dbe84d4a630e751e5618a22180ea8e4f8d143","tid":323904,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:26:40.000Z","msg":"火影完果陣仲有伏筆未交代，都唔知想點撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad735fc44ebaa4724296aee3455a5cd31e25a40c","tid":323904,"uid":82889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T19:34:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年地底泥嘅火影一完就上神檯<br />\n一堆人出黎話點好點好<br />\n比人屌嗰時又唔見呢班人出黎護航架wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好睇就好睇,唔好睇就係唔好睇<br />\n中意一套700集既漫畫唔代表集集都覺得好睇唔駛屌<br />\n老老柒柒乜撚野叫護航,一樣野明明唔好都要讚到佢好?<br />\n本身護航呢樣野就已經錯撚哂,點解可以講到理所當然要有咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2500726d039b8f1fe11d09b74570d525fcca0c52","tid":323904,"uid":16712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T19:43:03.000Z","msg":"火影最on9係d回憶  彌彥、帶土既回憶片段都唔知睇左幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee13eb7fe7bcb8191aab138af2c51457180b4c2","tid":323904,"uid":19837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T19:48:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當年地底泥嘅火影一完就上神檯<br />\n一堆人出黎話點好點好<br />\n比人屌嗰時又唔見呢班人出黎護航架wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好睇就好睇,唔好睇就係唔好睇<br />\n中意一套700集既漫畫唔代表集集都覺得好睇唔駛屌<br />\n老老柒柒乜撚野叫護航,一樣野明明唔好都要讚到佢好?<br />\n本身護航呢樣野就已經錯撚哂,點解可以講到理所當然要有咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n既然唔係集集都好睇即係有好有唔好<br />\n最弊d人就係將唔好睇嘅部份都要死拗做好睇呀嘛<br />\n呢個先係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁點解呢一班死都拗返生嘅人係嗰陣唔出黎撐呢？或者叫護航呢？我就係唔明呢點<br />\n唔好以為個個都好似你咁有思考能力先得架"},{"pid":"2a784a52cb86c063e7e2b0b1a6da2c6f567bb4f9","tid":323904,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T20:22:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/214804_c4781d11fff9556f0eb74108af1b7b3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F214804_c4781d11fff9556f0eb74108af1b7b3d.jpg&h=ee077ba4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個故sad到仆街"},{"pid":"e4a94b74a35946871bb275aa27ba625a20f42858","tid":323904,"uid":99028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T20:26:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"867b0806da4513f5936729c345a60d080666221f","tid":323904,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T07:11:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實無論係銷量，賺錢定係受歡迎人數，火影從來都無贏過one piece<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5b2d8e891e3a6081b7b4e21db848676bce1289","tid":323904,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T07:22:18.000Z","msg":"不過火影至少真係埋到個尾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/152118_24843fa2016b5e140fc9ccc9b6f04cce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F152118_24843fa2016b5e140fc9ccc9b6f04cce.jpg&h=7f841cf3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/152118_562f020ead991e59bfab889bf57f051d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F152118_562f020ead991e59bfab889bf57f051d.jpg&h=db765338&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57e1c5429480678662669f3ff95e6c3b0adb50ff","tid":323904,"uid":127075,"like":13,"dislike":7,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T07:46:32.000Z","msg":"火影d畫風分鏡講真好睇過op好撚多 <br />\n劇情方面op其實佢講咁9耐都係救同伴/救人做善事 跟本就唔撚係海賊黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成套野除左武器/惡魔果實之外 <br />\n跟本未出現過寶藏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係有寶藏出現過 但係路飛佢地都係光速洗曬<br />\n而火影當年第七班重逢都起碼有個重震撼係到<br />\n海賊劇情就唔係9叫就係船員講兩句路飛係成為海賊王既男人 之後就懶感人 再睇路飛起返身再打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又或者路飛成個傻仔咁 持住自己有光環自我中心到一個點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一見人就話要打<br />\n而鳴人都起碼嘴遁都有根有據 而鳴人目的係做世界仔 珍惜友情 一直追返mk佐都好正常姐<br />\n拎兩套垃圾黎比 但二揀一 睇火影好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nop想睇結局都loop多幾十個島都係同樣劇情輪迴等多十年囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時冇40歲都30啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起碼人地回憶幾百次都叫完左啦 至於佢個仔個套係佢徒弟畫 咪當gt咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f262cfbd636069821fbc14ea79157b602535974d","tid":323904,"uid":127075,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T07:52:15.000Z","msg":"至於人設方面 op有咩角色會好得過 自來也/鼬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算有都係尾田畫一百個角色都出黎唔同性格背景先比得上人地一個配角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n艾斯之死真係柒到唔敢再睇"},{"pid":"d1343d080220021fd7a14845b41d128ec87273e0","tid":323904,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8af652e6e3c92348144f48015385c42eac52b4f","tid":323904,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:20:26.000Z","msg":"火影比mk睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cebba10718833e74d3d686620597e69388ce9c2","tid":323904,"uid":124140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:26:47.000Z","msg":"hxh 已經再無後生MK討論鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲會留意既都開始做/做左呀叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b336f2b9e1c65b37ae3dc0f1453483b912191ca","tid":323904,"uid":111314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:27:07.000Z","msg":"老夫子完勝火影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a319c12acaa442ec9dbfe82836a13d894edf99","tid":323904,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:10:55.000Z","msg":"火影即食D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f899d582cb748bf313da07a2edf1980b11071652","tid":323904,"uid":21353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T17:48:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n柒撚到一個點，AC都唔撚閪鳩柒識轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87c8a15364856e89b771eec9b0de7305f2dac8f","tid":323904,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:58:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>火影完果陣仲有伏筆未交代，都唔知想點撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n例如呢？"},{"pid":"06e77b678ac232d52e47a1f3d35d51f1b53b07c3","tid":323904,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-2